I’m so excited for the launch of Good Mama!!! Who says pregnancy style can’t be sexy!? I am so proud of my @goodamerican maternity denim #GoodMama!! All you new mommies and mamas-to-be are going to be so chic in your Good Mamas!! Just dropped in sizes 00-24 on goodamerican.com!!

A post shared by Khloé (@khloekardashian) on Mar 15, 2018 at 8:59am PDT
